WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: c55LM0esoko

NOTE Language: en

00:04:38.624 --> 00:04:42.624
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:48.280
At the very outset,

00:04:48.625 --> 00:04:50.625
we have to know one thing,

00:04:51.080 --> 00:04:54.000
that truth is what it is.

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:56.799
We cannot organize it,

00:04:56.999 --> 00:04:59.480
we cannot order it,

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:04.400
we cannot conceptualize it also, with our human understanding.

00:05:08.320 --> 00:05:12.320
It is, it was and it will be.

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:16.680
The essence of all religions,

00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:19.200
if you bring it down

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:22.799
to the one-line essence,

00:05:22.999 --> 00:05:27.999
is this, that "seek the eternal",

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:33.999
and treat the transitory

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:38.320
with all understanding about it.

00:05:42.760 --> 00:05:46.760
The first part is the difficult one:

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:50.320
"seek the eternal".

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:52.560
Eternal is the truth.

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:55.200
And what is the truth?

00:05:55.999 --> 00:05:59.799
Now when I'm talking to you, you are all very well-versed and

00:05:59.999 --> 00:06:02.999
very well-educated people.

00:06:03.440 --> 00:06:06.440
I have to request you to have an open mind,

00:06:08.345 --> 00:06:10.345
a scientific outlook

00:06:11.320 --> 00:06:14.320
to see for yourself what I say,

00:06:14.801 --> 00:06:17.840
is the truth or not,

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:21.160
experience it,

00:06:21.960 --> 00:06:24.960
and treat all this talk as a hypothesis.

00:06:25.424 --> 00:06:28.944
And if it turns out to be the truth,

00:06:29.208 --> 00:06:32.328
then in all honesty we have to accept it.

00:06:37.280 --> 00:06:39.799
So there are two things

00:06:39.999 --> 00:06:43.480
which we may not accept,

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:45.920
but they exist.

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:48.999
One of them is

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:51.999
that all this universe,

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:55.160
all this creation,

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:58.680
is permeated by,

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:02.920
nourished by, looked after by

00:07:04.080 --> 00:07:07.799
all-pervading Power of God's love.

00:07:07.999 --> 00:07:11.999
In these modern times even to take God's name is too much.

00:07:13.720 --> 00:07:17.799
This is called as Paramachaitanya in Sanskrit language,

00:07:17.999 --> 00:07:19.799
in Koran it is called as ruh,

00:07:19.999 --> 00:07:23.520
in the Bible as the all-pervading Power of God's love,

00:07:23.760 --> 00:07:26.760
or the all-pervading Power of Divine.

00:07:27.320 --> 00:07:31.040
What we call as spirituality, divinity

00:07:31.280 --> 00:07:33.799
is the essence of that.

00:07:33.999 --> 00:07:35.799
This is first truth.

00:07:35.999 --> 00:07:38.999
And the second truth is

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:46.640
that we are not this body,

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:48.760
not this mind,

00:07:48.999 --> 00:07:50.799
not the emotions,

00:07:50.999 --> 00:07:53.799
not the ego, nor these thoughts.

00:07:53.999 --> 00:07:58.800
Beyond that we are the Spirit, we are the pure Spirit.

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:01.200
These are the two things

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:03.320
said in all religions,

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:06.999
whatever way they must have talked about.

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:13.440
In the olden times,

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:17.560
when seeking started in India...

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:21.999
India has certain privileges compared to other countries.

00:08:22.200 --> 00:08:24.400
Firstly the climate is so good,

00:08:24.640 --> 00:08:27.999
that you can live in a jungle without much trouble.

00:08:29.480 --> 00:08:31.520
While in the West we would say

00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:35.000
people started going outward, like a tree,

00:08:35.240 --> 00:08:39.840
the Indians started going downward into their roots.

00:08:40.040 --> 00:08:44.999
And they found out, long time back, Sahaja Yoga.

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:48.999
It's not a modern thing, it's an ancient

00:08:50.440 --> 00:08:54.720
[unscripted] method of getting union with the Divine,

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:56.320
which is yoga.

00:08:56.560 --> 00:08:58.799
"Sahaja" means "born with you"

00:08:58.999 --> 00:09:01.799
- "saha" is "with," "ja" "born."

00:09:01.999 --> 00:09:03.840
Born with you is the right

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:07.640
to get that union with the divine Power.

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:12.480
But "sahaja" also means "spontaneous,"

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:16.840
because this is the living power

00:09:17.999 --> 00:09:19.799
that works it out.

00:09:19.999 --> 00:09:22.999
There is a living power within us,

00:09:23.240 --> 00:09:25.000
which has made us

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:27.999
human beings from amoeba stage.

00:09:28.999 --> 00:09:32.999
And now there's another residual power,

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:36.799
which has to connect us to the Divine.

00:09:36.999 --> 00:09:39.999
This is the real meaning of the word "yoga."

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:42.999
And every human being has a right

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:47.999
to get united to that all-pervading Power.

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:52.520
So this is the last breakthrough of our evolution.

00:09:52.920 --> 00:09:57.280
At human level, as you know, we live in a relative world.

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:00.800
Some people say this is good, some people say that is good.

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:03.680
There's all a strife going on.

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:05.799
But if it is the absolute truth

00:10:05.999 --> 00:10:08.799
there should be no two opinions about it.

00:10:08.999 --> 00:10:10.840
So very humbly we must accept

00:10:11.040 --> 00:10:14.799
that we have not yet reached that absolute truth,

00:10:14.999 --> 00:10:17.360
which proves the existence of God,

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:20.799
which proves the existence of this all-pervading Power,

00:10:20.999 --> 00:10:23.240
which proves

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:26.480
the correctness of what

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:29.560
the great prophets, the great incarnations

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:31.680
have taught us.

00:10:31.920 --> 00:10:34.120
Of course religions have gone into diversions

00:10:34.360 --> 00:10:38.160
and deviations because of human effort,

00:10:38.999 --> 00:10:43.760
and they might have been

00:10:43.999 --> 00:10:46.840
apparently looking to be different,

00:10:47.400 --> 00:10:52.640
but they were just like flowers on the Tree of Life

00:10:52.960 --> 00:10:55.480
at different times, according to the timings.

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:58.720
Sanskrit the word is called as "samayachara".

00:10:59.680 --> 00:11:01.600
According to the time,

00:11:01.840 --> 00:11:03.520
the manifestation was there,

00:11:03.760 --> 00:11:08.760
but they were all created on one Tree of Life.

00:11:09.680 --> 00:11:11.320
But people plucked it,

00:11:11.560 --> 00:11:14.799
started saying, "This is mine. This is mine."

00:11:14.999 --> 00:11:17.999
and with the dead flowers they started fighting.

00:11:18.400 --> 00:11:21.400
That's how we see today the problem arising.

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:25.640
There was nothing wrong with these saints,

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:27.960
nothing wrong with the prophets,

00:11:28.440 --> 00:11:30.680
and nothing wrong with the incarnations.

00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:34.240
They all have done whatever was the best for us,

00:11:34.480 --> 00:11:36.799
and have tried to tell us from time to time

00:11:36.999 --> 00:11:40.799
at the time of our evolution, what we have to do.

00:11:40.999 --> 00:11:43.040
But mostly they have been dealing

00:11:43.280 --> 00:11:46.440
with the transitory things, how

00:11:46.680 --> 00:11:49.960
not to indulge into the transitory pleasures of life,

00:11:50.160 --> 00:11:52.999
but to seek the eternal.

00:11:54.999 --> 00:11:58.999
The second part of it is the "Seek the eternal."

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:01.799
That is, to get this yoga,

00:12:01.999 --> 00:12:05.680
to be united with this all-pervading Power,

00:12:05.920 --> 00:12:09.560
which gives you Self-Realization,

00:12:09.800 --> 00:12:11.640
to know the Self.

00:12:11.880 --> 00:12:14.880
"Know thy Self" - Christ has said it;

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:17.040
you are to be born again.

00:12:17.280 --> 00:12:20.880
Even in Sanskrit language, they call a person who is a realized soul

00:12:21.080 --> 00:12:23.799
as "dwijaha," means "born twice."

00:12:23.999 --> 00:12:28.999
They call a bird also as "dwijaha," meaning "born twice"

00:12:29.200 --> 00:12:30.880
- means first it's an egg

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:34.080
and then it becomes a free bird to fly out.

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:36.799
In the same way a "realized soul"

00:12:36.999 --> 00:12:39.680
means a person, a human being,

00:12:39.920 --> 00:12:42.999
who is connected with that all-pervading Power.

00:12:43.800 --> 00:12:46.160
Now what is the system within us

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:48.999
which has been created by God Almighty?

00:12:49.400 --> 00:12:52.999
Beautifully, because - not that He's our Creator,

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:54.880
but He is our loving Father,

00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:58.280
- and beautifully during our evolutionary process,

00:12:58.520 --> 00:13:01.600
He has created a very beautiful mechanism within us.

00:13:01.840 --> 00:13:07.999
I am sorry we don't have any diagram here of that,

00:13:08.240 --> 00:13:12.999
but that is described as "Tree of Life" in the Bible,

00:13:13.280 --> 00:13:15.799
it's described as "Asas" in Koran,

00:13:15.999 --> 00:13:18.799
is described as

00:13:18.999 --> 00:13:23.600
Kundalini in Sanskrit language.

00:13:23.840 --> 00:13:25.799
"Kundala" means "coils."

00:13:25.999 --> 00:13:28.799
Now this power of Kundalini,

00:13:28.999 --> 00:13:31.640
is the power

00:13:31.880 --> 00:13:35.960
which is the power of pure desire.

00:13:36.960 --> 00:13:39.960
All other desires are impure.

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:43.720
You know the law of economics is that

00:13:46.360 --> 00:13:49.600
in general, wants are not satiable.

00:13:49.999 --> 00:13:52.240
Today we want to have a table, then want to have a chair,

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:54.640
then want to have a car, then want to have a house;

00:13:54.880 --> 00:13:56.760
whatever we get, we are not satisfied with it.

00:13:56.999 --> 00:13:58.440
We jump from one to another.

00:13:58.680 --> 00:14:00.880
The reason is, whatever we desire

00:14:01.080 --> 00:14:03.640
is not the pure desire.

00:14:03.880 --> 00:14:07.880
The pure desire within us, whether you are aware of it or not,

00:14:08.200 --> 00:14:11.640
is to become one with the divine Power.

00:14:11.880 --> 00:14:14.799
And unless and until this desire is fulfilled,

00:14:14.999 --> 00:14:18.640
you can never have that satisfaction,

00:14:18.880 --> 00:14:21.720
that contentment of a saint.

00:14:21.960 --> 00:14:27.040
So this is the work one had to do.

00:14:27.600 --> 00:14:32.160
In the early days thousands of years back,

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:35.480
all over the world there were realized souls.

00:14:35.840 --> 00:14:38.799
We can start right from Abraham,

00:14:38.999 --> 00:14:42.999
to Moses, to Confucius.

00:14:43.480 --> 00:14:46.960
In India there were many great saints, Adi-Nath;

00:14:47.160 --> 00:14:49.760
from that nathpanthis they were called as.

00:14:49.999 --> 00:14:53.960
Their job was just to give awakening to people.

00:14:54.160 --> 00:14:56.799
At the time of Rama, His father-in-law

00:14:56.999 --> 00:14:59.440
was Janaka who was a king,

00:14:59.680 --> 00:15:03.799
but regarded as a very detached person, Vaidehi(?).

00:15:03.999 --> 00:15:10.120
and one disciple came to him, asked him for Self-Realization.

00:15:10.520 --> 00:15:12.440
He said, "You can ask for my kingdom,

00:15:12.680 --> 00:15:14.799
but it is not easy to give you Self-Realization."

00:15:14.999 --> 00:15:17.999
He said, "Why?" He said, "The time has not come."

00:15:18.920 --> 00:15:21.240
"So when will the time come?" He said, "Kali Yuga"

00:15:21.480 --> 00:15:22.999
- that's modern times.

00:15:23.240 --> 00:15:27.160
"This is the time when people will be

00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:29.400
living under illusions,

00:15:29.640 --> 00:15:33.120
subranth, and they will be

00:15:33.880 --> 00:15:36.999
under shock of destruction.

00:15:37.480 --> 00:15:39.880
They will not be able to solve their problems,

00:15:40.080 --> 00:15:41.960
and then they will

00:15:42.160 --> 00:15:45.400
seek the truth.

00:15:45.680 --> 00:15:49.799
And many of them who today are roaming about

00:15:49.999 --> 00:15:53.999
in the hills and dales, in the mountains Himalayas,

00:15:54.400 --> 00:15:58.000
will settle down as householders

00:15:58.320 --> 00:16:00.999
and they will get their Self-Realization."

00:16:01.240 --> 00:16:03.680
That is the time today.

00:16:03.920 --> 00:16:07.280
Whatever is said about the Last Judgment,

00:16:07.520 --> 00:16:09.799
this is the time for that Last Judgment.

00:16:09.999 --> 00:16:11.999
Also in Koran it is said

00:16:12.320 --> 00:16:15.799
that "At the time of your Resurrection your hands will speak,

00:16:15.999 --> 00:16:18.120
and they will give witness against you."

00:16:18.360 --> 00:16:21.400
Exactly this happens in Sahaja Yoga.

00:16:21.640 --> 00:16:25.080
The surah that is in Koran called as sashti yoga,

00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:28.680
it's surprising how Mohammed Sahib clearly said about it.

00:16:28.920 --> 00:16:33.040
He also said, "You won't believe it, because you are too arrogant.

00:16:33.320 --> 00:16:35.880
Because you won't be able to see that,

00:16:36.080 --> 00:16:38.799
you will be moving in another direction of fanaticism."

00:16:38.999 --> 00:16:40.720
Clearly He has said it.

00:16:40.960 --> 00:16:44.240
But as it is, nobody likes

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:47.640
to really go into the details of it

00:16:47.999 --> 00:16:51.920
and to find what is between the lines.

00:16:52.120 --> 00:16:54.440
That also is a very subtle thing.

00:16:54.680 --> 00:16:57.240
For that we have to become subtle beings,

00:16:57.600 --> 00:16:59.200
and to become that subtle being

00:16:59.440 --> 00:17:02.999
you have to get your Self-realization.

00:17:03.320 --> 00:17:08.240
At the time in the beginning, I would say, when they were searching,

00:17:08.999 --> 00:17:11.999
they went through their sympathetic nervous system,

00:17:12.280 --> 00:17:16.040
praying to God or doing their Vedas and all those things.

00:17:16.480 --> 00:17:19.080
And what they saw were the different deities

00:17:19.400 --> 00:17:23.280
sitting on the different chakras on the subtle centers,

00:17:23.520 --> 00:17:26.400
so they started talking about the deities.

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:31.999
So people started worshipping the deities.

00:17:34.280 --> 00:17:36.799
They wanted to have

00:17:36.999 --> 00:17:41.640
the nectar, the honey of the flower,

00:17:41.880 --> 00:17:46.280
but they started talking about the flower, worshipping the flower.

00:17:46.560 --> 00:17:49.799
So some people afterwards found it

00:17:49.999 --> 00:17:53.200
that it was not proper, like Buddha, Mahavira,

00:17:53.440 --> 00:17:55.960
Mohammed Sahib, Nanaka;

00:17:56.160 --> 00:17:59.880
all of them found that it's not proper to talk about the flowers,

00:18:00.080 --> 00:18:01.840
because people get lost.

00:18:02.040 --> 00:18:03.880
So better talk about the honey.

00:18:04.080 --> 00:18:07.799
So one was sakara, that is,

00:18:07.999 --> 00:18:10.440
with the form - another formless.

00:18:10.800 --> 00:18:13.799
So nirakara, they started talking about the formless.

00:18:13.999 --> 00:18:16.999
This was also talk, and talk, and talk.

00:18:17.200 --> 00:18:21.999
But to reach the honey you have to be a bee,

00:18:22.600 --> 00:18:24.999
and that's what is Self-realization is.

00:18:25.240 --> 00:18:28.440
Now this Kundalini is placed in the triangular bone,

00:18:28.680 --> 00:18:31.999
which is called as "sacrum" in the medical term.

00:18:32.680 --> 00:18:35.680
In Latin, "sacrum" means "sacred."

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:37.720
That means the Greeks knew about it,

00:18:37.960 --> 00:18:40.880
otherwise why should they call it a sacred bone?

00:18:41.280 --> 00:18:44.000
This Kundalini is awakened

00:18:44.240 --> 00:18:46.320
as a living process,

00:18:46.560 --> 00:18:49.760
like the seed sprouts when it is put in the Mother Earth;

00:18:49.999 --> 00:18:54.799
spontaneously rises, passes through six centers,

00:18:54.999 --> 00:18:57.120
the seventh center is below.

00:18:57.360 --> 00:19:01.040
And the seventh center is responsible for our excretion.

00:19:01.480 --> 00:19:04.440
It stops its function when it starts rising.

00:19:04.680 --> 00:19:06.480
So another myth

00:19:06.720 --> 00:19:09.360
which says that the sex has any part to play in our ascent

00:19:09.600 --> 00:19:10.800
is absolutely wrong,

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:15.040
because the center of sex which is the seventh center

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:17.999
is lower than the Kundalini.

00:19:19.880 --> 00:19:22.760
Then it rises, pierces through six centers.

00:19:22.999 --> 00:19:27.799
And the sixth center is placed on the fontanel bone area,

00:19:27.999 --> 00:19:30.520
where it was a soft bone once upon a time.

00:19:30.760 --> 00:19:33.040
But as you grow,

00:19:33.280 --> 00:19:35.560
through your sympathetic activity

00:19:35.800 --> 00:19:39.800
you develop two institutions in your head.

00:19:40.040 --> 00:19:43.160
From the right activity which is, we can call

00:19:43.400 --> 00:19:47.999
the power of action, you develop your ego like a balloon.

00:19:48.999 --> 00:19:51.480
And from the left side

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:53.799
which is your conditionings,

00:19:53.999 --> 00:19:56.280
you develop another balloon

00:19:56.520 --> 00:19:58.720
which is called as "superego" in English language,

00:19:58.960 --> 00:20:01.720
but in Sanskrit is "mana."

00:20:01.999 --> 00:20:07.120
Both of them join like this, sometimes overlap each other,

00:20:07.440 --> 00:20:10.600
and the bone becomes calcified.

00:20:10.840 --> 00:20:13.999
So now you are like an egg, I would say.

00:20:15.520 --> 00:20:18.999
Then when the Kundalini rises,

00:20:19.999 --> 00:20:23.440
when the Kundalini rises, She passes through this center

00:20:23.680 --> 00:20:28.999
which is placed between the optic chiasma, known as Agnya Chakra,

00:20:30.560 --> 00:20:33.560
which sometimes people call it as "third eye."

00:20:33.999 --> 00:20:37.080
And this center sucks in

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:40.799
these two institutions,

00:20:40.999 --> 00:20:42.999
opening the limbic area,

00:20:43.440 --> 00:20:46.720
and through which the Kundalini comes out,

00:20:46.960 --> 00:20:49.720
and you can feel the cool breeze coming out of your head,

00:20:49.960 --> 00:20:52.120
the actualization of the baptism.

00:20:52.400 --> 00:20:55.960
It's an actualization, it's not just a certificate.

00:20:58.440 --> 00:21:01.920
So, like every instrument has to be connected to the mains,

00:21:02.120 --> 00:21:04.999
you get connected with that subtle energy.

00:21:05.960 --> 00:21:07.999
And because this is the seat of your Spirit,

00:21:08.280 --> 00:21:11.080
but the seat in human beings resides in their heart,

00:21:11.640 --> 00:21:14.799
immediately the Spirit,

00:21:14.999 --> 00:21:18.000
start emitting light

00:21:18.320 --> 00:21:21.280
on your central nervous system.

00:21:21.520 --> 00:21:23.960
This is a very important point one must know.

00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:28.000
So you cannot understand it through your mental activity,

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:31.960
but through your evolutionary process,

00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:38.480
you manifest a new awareness on your central nervous system.

00:21:38.720 --> 00:21:42.120
And this awareness is called - in the Christian

00:21:43.560 --> 00:21:45.960
tradition in the olden times

00:21:46.160 --> 00:21:47.799
