00:41:13.040 --> 00:41:15.680
- My son-in-law has written a nice book about

00:41:15.920 --> 00:41:18.320
Manasarovar and this thing, and he went round

00:41:18.560 --> 00:41:20.200
and he has studied Buddhism,

00:41:20.440 --> 00:41:23.799
and he has gone to the caves where the earlier Buddhists lived.

00:41:23.999 --> 00:41:26.360
