00:41:31.200 --> 00:41:33.960
when the quarrel started with Mahayana, this, that.

00:41:34.160 --> 00:41:38.799
They formulated it, organized it, and this, and all that.

00:41:38.999 --> 00:41:41.799
But actually if you see to it,

00:41:41.999 --> 00:41:44.120
Buddha Himself

00:41:44.360 --> 00:41:47.999
is one of the part of the Kundalini.

00:41:48.400 --> 00:41:50.999
You have to use His name;

00:41:52.840 --> 00:41:56.920
He is the one who controls our ego, in evolution.

