Just works out. It's a living process of a living energy.

00:53:20.080 --> 00:53:21.840
- Now, you explain...

00:53:22.040 --> 00:53:24.799
- Just wondering if You think there's a difference

00:53:24.999 --> 00:53:27.799
between the Eastern and Western psyche;

00:53:27.999 --> 00:53:30.960
and if You do, what do You think the differences are?

00:53:31.160 --> 00:53:32.999
- Yes.

00:53:35.040 --> 00:53:39.999
Now the Western movement has been outward,

00:53:40.640 --> 00:53:42.200
like a tree,

00:53:42.440 --> 00:53:45.440
the whole civilization grew up.

00:53:45.680 --> 00:53:48.680
But it must seek its roots.

00:53:49.320 --> 00:53:52.520
To My eye there's not two things, East and West -

00:53:52.760 --> 00:53:54.920
the roots are the same as the tree;

00:53:55.120 --> 00:53:59.720
and if the tree does not find out its roots, it will be destroyed.

00:54:00.520 --> 00:54:02.680
Both are essential,

00:54:02.999 --> 00:54:05.360
complementary to each other.

00:54:06.640 --> 00:54:08.999
But because, as I told you, the climate in India

00:54:09.280 --> 00:54:11.520
has been quite kind,

00:54:12.040 --> 00:54:16.680
they went more into the search of themselves - "why are we here?"

00:54:17.999 --> 00:54:19.280
- instead of fighting the nature.

00:54:19.600 --> 00:54:23.999
But if you see the - I mean in London if you have to go out,

00:54:24.200 --> 00:54:27.480
you take at least fifteen minutes just to put on all your weapons

00:54:27.720 --> 00:54:30.120
to fight the climate there.

00:54:33.999 --> 00:54:37.680
In our country you can just walk out, no problem.

00:54:37.920 --> 00:54:40.080
So we didn't have to fight the nature,

00:54:40.400 --> 00:54:42.480
so that question was over;

00:54:42.720 --> 00:54:45.999
and it was a very beautiful country,

00:54:46.200 --> 00:54:47.999
full of fruits and things,

00:54:48.600 --> 00:54:52.480
so they could live in the jungles very well.

00:54:52.720 --> 00:54:54.720
Even now if you go,

00:54:54.999 --> 00:54:58.560
at the foothill of Himalayas you'll find all kinds of flowers,

00:54:58.920 --> 00:55:00.200
beautiful things there are.

00:55:00.440 --> 00:55:03.360
Of course now it's destroyed, because of civilization.

00:55:03.600 --> 00:55:06.360
So the people indulged more in finding out

00:55:06.640 --> 00:55:09.640
what is within us,

00:55:09.999 --> 00:55:12.240
and that's how they did it.

00:55:12.480 --> 00:55:14.999
So the search which is outside through science

00:55:15.200 --> 00:55:19.480
has to be substantiated and nourished by spirituality -

00:55:19.880 --> 00:55:21.920
it's very important.

00:55:22.480 --> 00:55:25.560
So these are part and parcel of the same.

00:55:25.960 --> 00:55:29.280
God has made only one world, one world.

00:55:29.600 --> 00:55:32.999
He didn't make many nations, we have done it.

00:55:33.200 --> 00:55:35.799
And sometimes I feel we were moved like criminals

00:55:35.999 --> 00:55:37.799
with our number-plate, you see,

00:55:37.999 --> 00:55:40.720
the passport number, this number, that number.

00:55:40.960 --> 00:55:43.999
God didn't make that way, it's our idea;

00:55:46.520 --> 00:55:49.799
because we laugh the same way,

00:55:49.999 --> 00:55:51.799
we smile the same way,

00:55:51.999 --> 00:55:54.920
we love the same way, everything is the same.

00:55:55.360 --> 00:55:57.120
But He had to create variety of faces,

00:55:57.400 --> 00:55:59.560
otherwise we would have been bored stiff!

00:56:08.440 --> 00:56:10.799
You'll be surprised, we have those forty nations I said,

00:56:10.999 --> 00:56:13.640
specially Russians.

00:56:13.880 --> 00:56:16.640
I must say a word for Russians specially, you see.

00:56:17.160 --> 00:56:20.999
Whatever may have been the mistakes of their

00:56:22.480 --> 00:56:24.840
dominating

00:56:25.600 --> 00:56:28.999
administrations and things, whatever they had,

00:56:29.999 --> 00:56:32.000
there's one thing good:

00:56:32.240 --> 00:56:35.360
as they didn't deal with politics and other things, you see,

00:56:35.600 --> 00:56:38.640
they put their minds to search within.

00:56:38.880 --> 00:56:42.640
They're very well-read people, very well-educated,

00:56:43.160 --> 00:56:45.680
very deep scientists also,

00:56:45.920 --> 00:56:48.080
but all of them have one mind in the science

00:56:48.360 --> 00:56:50.880
and another mind towards the Spirit.

00:56:51.080 --> 00:56:53.799
And I was amazed when I went there to Leningrad

00:56:53.999 --> 00:56:55.640
and they had never heard about Me,

00:56:55.880 --> 00:56:58.440
because there are no books available on Sahaja Yoga,

00:56:58.680 --> 00:57:01.560
or I've never written any books so far.

00:57:02.000 --> 00:57:04.240
There were two thousand people sitting outside

00:57:04.480 --> 00:57:06.999
and two thousand inside, in the hall.

00:57:07.200 --> 00:57:10.240
And after the lecture I gave Realization there

00:57:10.480 --> 00:57:13.800
- of course, this Realization works out en masse -

00:57:14.000 --> 00:57:18.999
and when they came out, they all asked Me, "Mother, what about us?"

00:57:19.280 --> 00:57:21.600
I said, "I'm sorry, the hall is small.

00:57:21.880 --> 00:57:24.320
If you can come tomorrow in this ground, I'll be here."

00:57:24.560 --> 00:57:27.080
Next morning I went there, the two thousand outside ones

00:57:27.400 --> 00:57:30.400
and inside ones all were there to meet Me.

00:57:30.720 --> 00:57:33.480
And now it has become sort of an,

00:57:33.880 --> 00:57:38.000
you can say, a kind of a big wave of Sahaja Yoga.

00:57:39.360 --> 00:57:44.880
They sent their people for filming in India,

00:57:45.080 --> 00:57:49.280
and they have accepted us as an independent organization

00:57:49.520 --> 00:57:52.640
for medical treatment, for education.

00:57:52.920 --> 00:57:55.520
They are going to give us a big house,

00:57:55.760 --> 00:57:59.800
everything, I mean whatever we want - the government.

00:58:02.840 --> 00:58:06.520
So sort of they were just waiting for it,

00:58:06.880 --> 00:58:09.520
just waiting for it.

00:58:11.360 --> 00:58:13.999
- Tell.
- In week of...

00:58:14.400 --> 00:58:17.799
I'm getting [many signs of] people who would like to ask questions.

00:58:17.999 --> 00:58:21.160
That, that's fine, but is there anybody else

00:58:21.400 --> 00:58:23.520
liking to ask a question?

00:58:23.760 --> 00:58:27.799
I didn't explain earlier that Mother is a medical doctor,

00:58:27.999 --> 00:58:30.840
so there may be questions, say, connecting,

00:58:31.040 --> 00:58:34.799
you know, healing with what She's talking about.

00:58:34.999 --> 00:58:36.799
And since She's talked about politics,

00:58:36.999 --> 00:58:39.799
I forgot to mention that She is the wife of,

00:58:39.999 --> 00:58:42.480
I think, the senior-most public servant in the United Nations.

00:58:42.720 --> 00:58:43.920
He's Secretary General,

00:58:44.120 --> 00:58:47.760
he's the senior-most Secretary-General of the UN.

00:58:47.999 --> 00:58:52.960
- Of the United Nations. So if you like to ask about politics even,

00:58:53.160 --> 00:58:55.640
She's very well-informed.

00:58:55.880 --> 00:58:57.960
-What's his name?

00:58:58.560 --> 00:59:00.560
- And on top of that I forgot to welcome

00:59:00.800 --> 00:59:05.320
- Ah, it's rather difficult then...
- those who've come from within the

00:59:05.920 --> 00:59:09.760
Sahaja Yoga community; that I welcome you all,

00:59:09.999 --> 00:59:11.720
those who come from that community,

00:59:11.960 --> 00:59:13.840
who may have particular questions

00:59:14.040 --> 00:59:15.960
that they'd like to ask You in this context,

00:59:16.160 --> 00:59:18.799
and by all means feel free about that,

00:59:18.999 --> 00:59:22.640
before we get back to those who want to ask You second questions -

00:59:22.880 --> 00:59:25.640
Anybody here? John.

00:59:27.999 --> 00:59:31.240
We've all had experiences. Generally I find

00:59:31.480 --> 00:59:33.799
- and I've explored experience to some extent -

00:59:33.999 --> 00:59:37.760
my experiences seem to be limited by

00:59:37.999 --> 00:59:40.040
my senses, my physical presence here.

00:59:40.280 --> 00:59:43.799
And if there is this all-pervading Power,

00:59:43.999 --> 00:59:46.999
that is something which is transcendent to my senses,

00:59:47.200 --> 00:59:50.880
it seems to me paradoxical. How can I experience this,

00:59:51.080 --> 00:59:55.999
when all my experience is bound by my senses?

00:59:56.320 --> 00:59:59.240
I mean, is there a real experience of that?

00:59:59.480 --> 01:00:01.360
You see, I still don't know that.

01:00:01.600 --> 01:00:02.920
Experience of what?

01:00:03.120 --> 01:00:05.880
Well, You said that a person can have experience of this power,

01:00:06.080 --> 01:00:09.680
this transcendental power, when this is something I suppose I know.

01:00:09.960 --> 01:00:11.760
Yes, of course, of course it is there.

01:00:11.999 --> 01:00:14.000
And not only that, but you go beyond your mind,

01:00:14.240 --> 01:00:17.480
because you reach a state which is called as thoughtless awareness,

01:00:17.720 --> 01:00:20.480
thoughtless awareness. You are aware,

01:00:20.999 --> 01:00:22.400
but there's no thought.

01:00:22.640 --> 01:00:25.799
For example, a thought rises within us and then it falls,

01:00:25.999 --> 01:00:28.120
and another thought rises and falls.

01:00:28.360 --> 01:00:31.999
We live either in the past or in the future;

01:00:32.400 --> 01:00:35.920
on the cusp of these thoughts we are dancing all the time.

01:00:36.120 --> 01:00:40.120
So when the Kundalini rises these thoughts become lean,

01:00:40.360 --> 01:00:42.800
and there's a space in between which is the present,

01:00:43.000 --> 01:00:46.000
which in Sanskrit is called as "vilamba".

01:00:46.240 --> 01:00:49.840
So when the Kundalini rises

01:00:50.040 --> 01:00:51.760
you become thoughtless.

01:00:51.999 --> 01:00:53.360
If you want to think you can think it,

01:00:53.600 --> 01:00:55.799
but if you don't want to think you are in thoughtless awareness.

01:00:55.999 --> 01:00:57.840
That's the samadhi state, that's the state

01:00:58.040 --> 01:01:00.799
of what you call is the meditative state,

01:01:00.999 --> 01:01:04.600
where first is called as "thoughtless awareness".

01:01:04.840 --> 01:01:07.640
In Sanskrit it's called as "nirvichara samadhi".

01:01:07.999 --> 01:01:10.000
Then the second state that is achieved

01:01:10.240 --> 01:01:15.080
is called as "doubtless awareness," called as "Nirvikalpa" - means

01:01:16.560 --> 01:01:18.560
you are so evolved that

01:01:18.800 --> 01:01:22.040
you have no doubts about it, you just work it out.

01:01:22.999 --> 01:01:24.640
And in a sense that it's beyond,

01:01:24.880 --> 01:01:27.080
even that it's an experience, it's also beyond experience.

01:01:27.320 --> 01:01:29.799
It's like an experience beyond experience,

01:01:29.999 --> 01:01:31.880
because that is an experience of something

01:01:32.080 --> 01:01:33.880
on which all other experiences are based.

01:01:34.080 --> 01:01:35.799
- Yes, it is beyond that, of course.

01:01:35.999 --> 01:01:38.799
So in a sense it's like an end of experience, at the same time.

01:01:38.999 --> 01:01:42.799
No, no, no, no! The experience is of the feeling

01:01:42.999 --> 01:01:46.799
this all-pervading Power, is precise - all right?

01:01:46.999 --> 01:01:49.240
And then the experience

01:01:49.480 --> 01:01:53.999
of feeling your centers on your fingertips, to be precise.

01:01:54.280 --> 01:01:55.999
Then the experience is

01:01:56.200 --> 01:01:59.680
that you can become thoughtlessly aware.

01:01:59.920 --> 01:02:04.880
Then the experience is that if you want to work on other people,

01:02:05.080 --> 01:02:08.560
you find that you can find out about their own centers,

01:02:08.800 --> 01:02:10.840
and you can raise their Kundalini

01:02:11.040 --> 01:02:13.320
and you can give them Realization.

01:02:13.560 --> 01:02:15.799
So you start experiencing yourself,

01:02:15.999 --> 01:02:19.920
like you enter into a big palace - that's yourself.

01:02:20.120 --> 01:02:22.480
So first you enter into the hall,

01:02:22.720 --> 01:02:24.720
then you see other things and then other things,

01:02:24.960 --> 01:02:27.080
and you're amazed at yourself.

01:02:27.800 --> 01:02:32.360
It's like that. It's a new dimensions into which you enter.

01:02:35.520 --> 01:02:36.799
-Yes, state...

01:02:36.999 --> 01:02:40.320
Yes, this is actually more a political question, but

01:02:40.560 --> 01:02:41.799
one of the things that fascinates me

01:02:41.999 --> 01:02:43.160
about world politics at the moment

01:02:43.400 --> 01:02:46.120
actually seems to be the Hindu fundamentalism.

01:02:46.360 --> 01:02:47.760
Possibly You give us ....

01:02:47.999 --> 01:02:50.360
- What's it?
- [unclear] Hindu fundamentalism.

01:02:50.600 --> 01:02:53.799
Would You like to comment on Hindu fundamentalism?

01:02:53.999 --> 01:02:57.640
They are just like anybody else, what's there to comment?

01:02:59.400 --> 01:03:02.920
But it was very late they started.

01:03:03.120 --> 01:03:06.520
The reason was also because of the Sikh aggression.

01:03:06.760 --> 01:03:10.240
The Sikhs started killing people in Punjab,

01:03:10.999 --> 01:03:13.999
saying that

01:03:14.200 --> 01:03:16.400
"you are Hindus".

01:03:16.640 --> 01:03:18.840
So they formed themselves into a group,

01:03:19.040 --> 01:03:21.600
"All right, we are Hindus, so what?"

01:03:21.840 --> 01:03:25.280
to protect themselves, more sort of protective way they started it.

01:03:25.760 --> 01:03:28.960
But whatever it is I don't agree with that much,

01:03:29.160 --> 01:03:31.799
that why don't they get Realization?

01:03:31.999 --> 01:03:34.999
- nobody can touch you.

01:03:35.440 --> 01:03:38.920
But they'll come round, I think, all of them one day.

01:03:41.999 --> 01:03:43.560
- Alex.

01:03:43.800 --> 01:03:48.800
When the realized people write up the accounts of their experience,

01:03:49.440 --> 01:03:52.160
can you discern in those - and You might like to comment -

01:03:52.400 --> 01:03:54.520
whether there are any common elements

01:03:54.760 --> 01:03:57.320
in what I might call in the Western thinking,

01:03:57.560 --> 01:04:00.560
triggers for the surrendered life.

01:04:00.800 --> 01:04:05.200
In other words, experiences that they might have had which led them

01:04:05.440 --> 01:04:08.680
into the experience of enlightenment.

01:04:08.999 --> 01:04:10.320
I'm interested in this question

01:04:10.560 --> 01:04:12.799
from the point of view of the alcoholic, actually,

01:04:12.999 --> 01:04:16.799
how it is that an alcoholic does undergo a cognitive change,

01:04:16.999 --> 01:04:21.080
a very pronounced cognitive change when he's being rehabilitated,

01:04:21.320 --> 01:04:23.799
particularly in a program like the AA.

01:04:23.999 --> 01:04:27.560
In the enlightened regime,

01:04:27.800 --> 01:04:31.120
are there triggers or indications

01:04:31.360 --> 01:04:33.799
that enlightenment might be just around the corner,

01:04:33.999 --> 01:04:37.720
or something which led you into it? Does that make sense?

01:04:38.200 --> 01:04:39.360
- Triggering what?

01:04:39.600 --> 01:04:42.799
Triggers, now trigger is are what you pull when you shoot guns!

01:04:42.999 --> 01:04:46.600
I know, I know that part.

01:04:47.999 --> 01:04:51.280
But one other way of referring to these triggers

01:04:51.520 --> 01:04:55.520
is what we call predisposing factors

01:04:55.760 --> 01:04:58.240
for enlightenment.

01:04:58.480 --> 01:05:00.440
Are people

01:05:00.680 --> 01:05:03.480
because of the evolutionary process

01:05:03.720 --> 01:05:07.840
in a position where there are more predisposing factors

01:05:08.040 --> 01:05:10.280
for them to become enlightened,

01:05:10.520 --> 01:05:13.520
or are there certain things which could happen in their lives?

01:05:13.760 --> 01:05:17.800
Like You use the example of the Kali Yuga, it's so oppressive,

01:05:18.000 --> 01:05:19.600
so you know, suddenly you realize

01:05:19.840 --> 01:05:21.640
something desperately has to be done.

01:05:21.880 --> 01:05:24.799
But I must tell you that the Divine is so anxious

01:05:24.999 --> 01:05:28.920
to give you realization, it doesn't bother about anything.

01:05:29.999 --> 01:05:33.520
And we can compare our evolutionary process

01:05:33.760 --> 01:05:35.999
to a spacecraft.

01:05:36.320 --> 01:05:38.840
In a spacecraft like Sputnik or anything

01:05:39.040 --> 01:05:40.920
there's a container, first container,

01:05:41.120 --> 01:05:43.600
and it has containers in it.

01:05:43.840 --> 01:05:47.999
So the first container, containing all other containers, flies.

01:05:48.600 --> 01:05:51.880
But when it goes up to a point

01:05:52.080 --> 01:05:55.480
it has a certain velocity, and then as you say, triggers

01:05:55.720 --> 01:05:57.760
- means there's an explosion,

01:05:57.999 --> 01:06:00.880
and the second container is thrown

01:06:01.080 --> 01:06:03.040
with a much greater velocity.

01:06:03.280 --> 01:06:05.799
Like that it happens. Now we are

01:06:05.999 --> 01:06:07.999
as the last container, we should think,

01:06:08.200 --> 01:06:11.240
and the triggering is so fast, I am Myself amazed

01:06:11.480 --> 01:06:13.600
at the working out of this.

01:06:13.840 --> 01:06:15.640
It is not bothered

01:06:15.880 --> 01:06:18.440
as to what you have done, anything you have sinned, so-called

01:06:18.720 --> 01:06:20.999
- your guilt is all nonsense now,

01:06:21.200 --> 01:06:23.799
everything is absolutely a nonsense.

01:06:23.999 --> 01:06:25.200
It just works out.

01:06:25.480 --> 01:06:27.799
You don't have to do any cleansing, nothing of the kind,

01:06:27.999 --> 01:06:29.640
it just works out.

01:06:29.880 --> 01:06:34.000
It's like a torrential, we can say rain of the grace.

01:06:35.999 --> 01:06:37.999
It is happening.

01:06:38.320 --> 01:06:41.720
But there are no common indications? It's just like going back...

01:06:41.960 --> 01:06:44.720
No, no, no, nothing;

01:06:44.960 --> 01:06:47.999
nothing of the kind, nothing.

01:06:52.480 --> 01:06:55.999
- As a practicing Sahaja yogi,

01:06:57.000 --> 01:07:01.600
I've experienced the benefits of thoughtless awareness

01:07:01.840 --> 01:07:03.799
and the benefits of Sahaja Yoga.

01:07:03.999 --> 01:07:07.280
What or how different would my life be

01:07:07.520 --> 01:07:09.760
or my experiences be,

01:07:09.999 --> 01:07:11.799
when I've attained doubtless awareness?

01:07:11.999 --> 01:07:14.799
Is that the aim also of the Sahaja yogi,

01:07:14.999 --> 01:07:17.799
to strive towards doubtless awareness?

01:07:17.999 --> 01:07:19.799
And then how different

01:07:19.999 --> 01:07:21.799
or what changes would I experience

01:07:21.999 --> 01:07:25.999
in doubtless awareness, when I am a practicing Sahaja yogini?

01:07:26.520 --> 01:07:30.440
In doubtless awareness when you rise from thoughtless awareness,

01:07:30.680 --> 01:07:32.520
what happens that you start growing,

01:07:32.760 --> 01:07:34.799
because only in present you grow.

01:07:34.999 --> 01:07:37.999
You start growing, and then

01:07:38.640 --> 01:07:42.080
you feel like doing it for others also.

01:07:42.320 --> 01:07:45.799
You want to help others, you want to talk about it, work it out.

01:07:45.999 --> 01:07:48.000
This is sort of a, the collective,

01:07:49.999 --> 01:07:53.400
we can say the collective generosity starts,

01:07:53.640 --> 01:07:57.280
and you start working it out for others, you talk to other people

01:07:57.480 --> 01:08:00.920
and you start raising their Kundalini, helping them and all that.

01:08:01.120 --> 01:08:04.799
As a result of that you can become very powerful.

01:08:04.999 --> 01:08:09.280
You can even control the elements, so many things you can control,

01:08:09.600 --> 01:08:11.640
and it's limitless,

01:08:11.880 --> 01:08:14.920
because it is something really

01:08:15.160 --> 01:08:19.520
that is, we can say is beyond our conception

01:08:19.760 --> 01:08:22.999
how far we can go. It's tremendous.

01:08:23.840 --> 01:08:25.920
Just to follow that,

01:08:26.120 --> 01:08:28.560
how would I personally work

01:08:28.800 --> 01:08:32.600
towards realizing this state more and more and more strongly,

01:08:32.999 --> 01:08:36.280
this state of doubtless awareness? How do I

01:08:36.520 --> 01:08:40.080
surrender myself more and more? What things would I do?

01:08:40.680 --> 01:08:43.720
For that Buddha has told you that "Sangam sharanam gacchami"

01:08:43.960 --> 01:08:46.480
- you have to come in the collective.

01:08:46.720 --> 01:08:50.080
It works in the collective, because it's the work of the collective.

01:08:50.440 --> 01:08:53.120
