01:10:12.999 --> 01:10:16.799
and this potter was busy kneading his clay

01:10:16.999 --> 01:10:19.160
to make pots.

01:10:19.600 --> 01:10:21.799
Namadeva saw him there,

01:10:21.999 --> 01:10:24.520
looked at him, he was so stunned.

01:10:24.760 --> 01:10:28.600
He says, "I came here to see the nirakara,

01:10:28.840 --> 01:10:32.120
to see the formless, and here it is in form."

01:10:32.640 --> 01:10:36.200
What an appreciation, what a adoration,

01:10:36.440 --> 01:10:38.999
and what an understanding of each other!

01:10:45.999 --> 01:10:48.720
But they were so few.

01:10:48.960 --> 01:10:52.160
They were all tortured and troubled, I must say, terrible things,

01:10:52.440 --> 01:10:55.480
because people didn't understand them.

01:10:56.640 --> 01:10:59.960
And whatever they say is the truth.

01:11:01.200 --> 01:11:04.720
Every word that they said is the truth.

