01:13:04.999 --> 01:13:07.520
to just read more and more and understand it more

01:13:07.760 --> 01:13:09.440
in an intellectual way.

01:13:09.680 --> 01:13:13.120
Now what role do You assign to this kind of pursuit,

01:13:13.360 --> 01:13:14.600
intellectual pursuit?

