01:13:18.920 --> 01:13:22.080
maybe they say, "Ah, not really," but they pursue the books.

01:13:22.320 --> 01:13:26.920
So what do You see, what's the role of pursuing text and books?

01:13:27.480 --> 01:13:29.920
You see, if you read books only,

01:13:30.120 --> 01:13:33.800
then you get lost in the words, not in reality.

01:13:34.999 --> 01:13:37.120
