01:23:27.200 --> 01:23:30.040
If you don't have the capital, how can you distribute it?

01:23:30.560 --> 01:23:32.999
But the capital of spirituality is important,

01:23:33.200 --> 01:23:36.160
not these worldly things - these are transitory.

01:23:38.280 --> 01:23:40.799
All these theories that look contradictory

01:23:40.999 --> 01:23:42.799
actually are integrated.

01:23:42.999 --> 01:23:47.799
All religions which look contradictory, they all integrate.

01:23:47.999 --> 01:23:50.799
Actually we get integrated within ourselves,

01:23:50.999 --> 01:23:53.999
complete integration takes place.

01:23:55.880 --> 01:23:59.080
